I [C]picked my guitar till my [F]fingers were [C]blistered
Blistered and bleeding [G7]and staining my [C]jeans[G7]
[C]Some tried to whip me [F]more didn’t than [C]did
And I’m proud of my dues and [G7]my guitar still has 6 [C]strings
Repeat #1
